de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.utilities.datastructures.hash

Class Unique<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gnu.trove.impl.hash.THash
      • gnu.trove.impl.hash.TObjectHash<E>
        • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.utilities.datastructures.hash.Unique<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable

    public class Unique<E>
extends gnu.trove.impl.hash.TObjectHash<E>
    This hash set is designed to keep only a unique copy of each object (hence its name). For this, the method addOrGet(E) is the key API, which allows retrieving existing values.
    Since:
    0.7.0
    Author:
    Erich Schubert
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
